%h2= name

%p.follow You can find and follow me as
%p.screenname
  %a(href="http://twitter.com/blindgaenger") @blindgaenger
%p.latest Here are some of my latest tweets

%ul.tweets
  - @tweets.each_with_index do |tweet, index|
    %li.tweet(class="tweet-#{index}")
      %a.icon(href="http://www.twitter.com/#{tweet.user}" target="_blank")
        %img(src="#{tweet.icon}" alt="#{tweet.user}" width=48 height=48)
      .content
        %a.user(href="http://www.twitter.com/#{tweet.user}" target="_blank")= tweet.user
        .text!= tweet.html
        %a.date(href="http://twitter.com/#{tweet.user}/status/#{tweet.id}" target="_blank")= tweet.time.strftime('%d %b')
        
%p.readmore
  %a(href="http://twitter.com/blindgaenger") Read more @blindgaenger
